snippet.title: Anti-Gun Senator Kevin de Leόn Makes Complete Fool Out Of Himself! Full Video

localized.description:
We are going to do our best to help spread the word on who should be voted out of office when election time comes. This guy has always been on the list, but his latest bill is just as dumb as he is. Senate Bill 808



SACRAMENTO -- Flanked by representatives from law enforcement and the Brady Campaign to Prevent Gun Violence, Senator Kevin de Leόn (D-Los Angeles) today unveiled legislation to ban the sale, manufacture, purchase and trafficking of plastic and self-assembled firearms -- often referred to as "ghost guns" -- in California.  Senate Bill 808 requires self-made or assembled guns to contain permanent pieces of metal and to be registered with the Department of Justice through a serial number and gun owner background check. - Full Video
